1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

The target image shows a structure composed of 6 blocks arranged in two layers.  There are two vertical blocks of a light yellow color, two smaller blocks of a green color, and one block of a red color. The green blocks are positioned horizontally on the top of the yellow blocks, with the red block positioned in between the yellow blocks on the second layer.

* Block Index 14 (light yellow, vertical)
* Block Index 2 (green, square)
* Block Index 6 (green, rectangular horizontal)
* Block Index 6 (green, rectangular horizontal)
* Block Index 3 (red, square)
